574
00:25:27,600 --> 00:25:28,600
You must be busy.

575
00:25:29,080 --> 00:25:30,880
I heard that you're in charge

576
00:25:30,960 --> 00:25:32,000
of the housing allotment too.

577
00:25:32,000 --> 00:25:33,000
Exactly.

578
00:25:33,240 --> 00:25:34,280
However, even if I'm busy,

579
00:25:34,480 --> 00:25:35,920
I still have to see you
when you ask me to.

580
00:25:37,520 --> 00:25:39,680
I have a favor to ask.

581
00:25:39,800 --> 00:25:40,840
A favor to ask?

582
00:25:41,240 --> 00:25:41,840
I mean,

583
00:25:41,960 --> 00:25:43,200
you can ask me for a favor at home

584
00:25:43,320 --> 00:25:44,600
or during a phone call.

585
00:25:45,080 --> 00:25:46,440
Why did you invite me to dinner?

586
00:25:46,600 --> 00:25:48,120
After only working for a few days here,

587
00:25:48,160 --> 00:25:49,680
you've mastered

588
00:25:49,760 --> 00:25:51,080
the unnecessary formalities, haven't you?

589
00:25:51,920 --> 00:25:52,960
Don't tease me.

590
00:25:54,240 --> 00:25:55,480
Actually, it's not about me.

591
00:25:55,880 --> 00:25:57,160
It's about a brother in the Squad.

592
00:25:58,120 --> 00:25:58,720
Well,

593
00:25:59,720 --> 00:26:00,840
there are so many people in the Squad.

594
00:26:00,960 --> 00:26:02,040
Are they all your brothers?

595
00:26:02,840 --> 00:26:04,040
Tell me

596
00:26:04,320 --> 00:26:05,080
about it now.

597
00:26:05,440 --> 00:26:06,720
There's a senior colleague

598
00:26:06,960 --> 00:26:08,200
named Cao Biao.

599
00:26:08,560 --> 00:26:09,480
Does the name ring a bell?

600
00:26:11,800 --> 00:26:12,640
He's from Shandong

601
00:26:12,640 --> 00:26:13,720
and he's a veteran too.

602
00:26:14,040 --> 00:26:14,680
Yes.

603
00:26:14,680 --> 00:26:16,200
He's a very honest man.

604
00:26:16,320 --> 00:26:17,320
There are three elderly people

605
00:26:17,320 --> 00:26:18,160
and three kids in his family.

606
00:26:18,240 --> 00:26:19,400
And they live in a two-room apartment.

607
00:26:19,480 --> 00:26:21,240
That's too small.

608
00:26:22,080 --> 00:26:23,720
His length of service
has met the criteria.

609
00:26:24,240 --> 00:26:26,680
Why didn't he
get housing again this time?

610
00:26:27,840 --> 00:26:28,440
Hongjun,

611
00:26:28,880 --> 00:26:29,960
you're in charge of the allotment.

612
00:26:30,240 --> 00:26:31,560
You must know the reason.

613
00:26:32,880 --> 00:26:33,720
I know.

614
00:26:35,440 --> 00:26:36,680
What criterion didn't he meet?

615
00:26:37,600 --> 00:26:38,680
He has met all the criteria.

616
00:26:39,720 --> 00:26:40,840
Then what's the reason?

617
00:26:41,120 --> 00:26:42,240
You're new here,

618
00:26:42,360 --> 00:26:43,480
there are lots of things you don't know,

619
00:26:43,600 --> 00:26:44,000
Chunsheng.

620
00:26:44,200 --> 00:26:44,600
Cheers.

621
00:26:48,400 --> 00:26:52,280
Do you know the Deputy Director, Mr. Xue?

622
00:26:54,440 --> 00:26:55,280
I remember him.

623
00:26:55,600 --> 00:26:56,600
He's tall

624
00:26:56,840 --> 00:26:58,440
and has an imposing manner.

625
00:26:59,640 --> 00:27:00,600
Xue

626
00:27:00,840 --> 00:27:02,720
used to be Cao Biao's
immediate supervisor.

627
00:27:03,000 --> 00:27:04,240
Then for some reason,

628
00:27:04,480 --> 00:27:05,600
they fell out.

629
00:27:06,000 --> 00:27:08,280
Cao Biao often complains
about Xue's malpractices

630
00:27:08,480 --> 00:27:09,760
to the General Administration.

631
00:27:09,880 --> 00:27:11,360
That's how they became enemies.

632
00:27:12,360 --> 00:27:13,200
That's it?

633
00:27:14,920 --> 00:27:15,840
Later,

634
00:27:16,000 --> 00:27:17,760
Xue came to see me and suggested

635
00:27:17,920 --> 00:27:19,960
that I shouldn't allot housing to Cao Biao.

636
00:27:21,160 --> 00:27:23,040
Isn't this abusing public power
to retaliate against a personal enemy?

637
00:27:23,720 --> 00:27:25,680
Some people are just this dishonorable.

638
00:27:26,080 --> 00:27:27,040
He's my superior,

639
00:27:27,040 --> 00:27:28,080
so I can't pretend that I don't understand it.

640
00:27:29,800 --> 00:27:30,760
Think about it.

641
00:27:31,040 --> 00:27:32,200
He's so narrow-minded.

642
00:27:32,800 --> 00:27:33,840
If I offend him,

643
00:27:34,480 --> 00:27:35,760
then he won't spare me.

644
00:27:36,600 --> 00:27:37,960
It's hard to deal with
despicable people like him.

645
00:27:38,240 --> 00:27:40,080
Then Cao Biao deserves no housing?

646
00:27:43,680 --> 00:27:44,240
Well,

647
00:27:44,600 --> 00:27:45,040
Chunsheng,

648
00:27:46,040 --> 00:27:47,080
it's very likely

649
00:27:47,080 --> 00:27:49,360
that Xue will be transferred
to the Trade Union next year.

650
00:27:49,600 --> 00:27:50,480
After he leaves,

651
00:27:50,480 --> 00:27:51,560
when we allot housing again,

652
00:27:51,800 --> 00:27:53,080
I'll give Cao Biao housing first.

653
00:27:53,720 --> 00:27:54,480
Is this okay?

654
00:27:56,040 --> 00:27:57,000
It's okay,

655
00:27:57,760 --> 00:27:59,360
but I find it a bit infuriating.

656
00:28:00,600 --> 00:28:02,040
How can Xue be such a big bully?

657
00:28:02,520 --> 00:28:04,360
Isn't this malpractice?

658
00:28:05,360 --> 00:28:06,320
Listen,

659
00:28:06,440 --> 00:28:08,080
there must be some truth

660
00:28:08,560 --> 00:28:09,440
in what Cao Biao has complained about.

661
00:28:10,200 --> 00:28:11,200
Well, Chunsheng,

662
00:28:11,360 --> 00:28:13,680
there are lots of things like this.

663
00:28:13,840 --> 00:28:15,320
It's out of our capacity.

664
00:28:15,520 --> 00:28:16,760
We're against malpractice,

665
00:28:16,840 --> 00:28:17,920
we have more work to do
and a long way to go.

666
00:28:18,600 --> 00:28:20,560
However, we can't act rashly.

667
00:28:20,800 --> 00:28:21,960
If the unity is undermined,

668
00:28:22,160 --> 00:28:23,280
then our work will be harder.

669
00:28:23,480 --> 00:28:24,480
Don't you think so?

670
00:28:26,520 --> 00:28:27,160
Yeah.

671
00:28:27,360 --> 00:28:28,720
Hongjun, what you said is right.

672
00:28:29,240 --> 00:28:29,680
Come on.

673
00:28:29,680 --> 00:28:31,080
Let's eat. The food is getting cold.

674
00:28:31,920 --> 00:28:32,720
Chunsheng,

675
00:28:32,840 --> 00:28:34,080
if there's nothing else,

676
00:28:34,080 --> 00:28:35,240
then I have to go now.

677
00:28:35,440 --> 00:28:36,760
Director Shao asked me

678
00:28:37,000 --> 00:28:39,080
to have dinner with the senior officials
of the Foreign Trade Bureau.

679
00:28:39,560 --> 00:28:40,600
When you asked me to come,

680
00:28:41,040 --> 00:28:42,760
I told them that
there was an emergency at home.

681
00:28:43,200 --> 00:28:44,360
But they said

682
00:28:44,360 --> 00:28:45,360
that no matter how late it is,

683
00:28:45,360 --> 00:28:46,600
I have to come.

684
00:28:46,840 --> 00:28:48,080
Hongjun, go ahead then.

685
00:28:48,080 --> 00:28:49,760
Don't let me get in the way of your work.

686
00:28:49,760 --> 00:28:51,200
Okay, Chunsheng, goodbye.

687
00:28:51,320 --> 00:28:52,080
Goodbye.

688
00:28:53,520 --> 00:28:54,200
Bye.

689
00:29:12,440 --> 00:29:15,000
Such a big meal today.

690
00:29:15,960 --> 00:29:17,160
You must be in a good mood.

691
00:29:20,840 --> 00:29:21,760
What happened?

692
00:29:22,200 --> 00:29:22,920
Nothing.

693
00:29:23,160 --> 00:29:24,360
Were you in trouble at work?

694
00:29:26,400 --> 00:29:27,400
I don't know

695
00:29:28,440 --> 00:29:29,720
what I can do with Chunsheng.

696
00:29:31,080 --> 00:29:31,960
What on earth has happened?

697
00:29:38,000 --> 00:29:39,040
There's a guy named Cao Biao

698
00:29:39,800 --> 00:29:40,880
in the Anti-smuggling Squad

699
00:29:41,160 --> 00:29:42,280
who has offended Mr. Xue.

700
00:29:42,640 --> 00:29:43,560
Xue

701
00:29:44,000 --> 00:29:45,320
made things hard for Cao

702
00:29:45,560 --> 00:29:47,160
and didn't allot housing
to him this time.

703
00:29:47,560 --> 00:29:49,080
Chunsheng came to see me for this.

704
00:29:49,080 --> 00:29:50,040
I said that I knew it,

705
00:29:50,360 --> 00:29:51,560
but there was nothing I could do.

706
00:29:51,840 --> 00:29:53,400
Xue has the support of the leaders,

707
00:29:53,640 --> 00:29:54,880
and he's notorious
for being narrow-minded.

708
00:29:55,080 --> 00:29:56,360
It's not worth it for me to offend him,

709
00:29:56,600 --> 00:29:57,560
right?

710
00:29:58,560 --> 00:29:59,600
Anyway, Xue

711
00:29:59,600 --> 00:30:01,000
will be transferred
to the Trade Union next year.

712
00:30:01,160 --> 00:30:02,200
After he leaves,

713
00:30:03,320 --> 00:30:05,160
it's very likely that I'll be his successor.

714
00:30:05,480 --> 00:30:06,760
At that time, I will allot housing

715
00:30:06,760 --> 00:30:07,840
to Cao Biao for sure.

716
00:30:08,400 --> 00:30:10,080
I thought Chunsheng had agreed with this.

717
00:30:10,360 --> 00:30:11,240
But guess what?

718
00:30:12,160 --> 00:30:13,520
Chunsheng called me at noon

719
00:30:13,720 --> 00:30:14,920
and asked me to eat

720
00:30:15,000 --> 00:30:17,600
in the Sichuan restaurant
near our workplace.

721
00:30:18,080 --> 00:30:19,560
I went there and found

722
00:30:20,960 --> 00:30:21,960
that Xue was there too.

723
00:30:22,640 --> 00:30:24,200
Shortly afterwards, Cao Biao arrived too

724
00:30:24,280 --> 00:30:25,560
and Xue was stunned.

725
00:30:26,120 --> 00:30:27,760
Then Chunsheng said something very blunt

726
00:30:27,760 --> 00:30:28,840
to Xue in front of me.

727
00:30:28,960 --> 00:30:29,600
He said

728
00:30:30,040 --> 00:30:30,840
that there were rumors out there

729
00:30:31,120 --> 00:30:33,040
that Xue and Cao

730
00:30:33,240 --> 00:30:35,280
had problems,

731
00:30:35,280 --> 00:30:36,480
and that was why Xue
retaliated against Cao.

732
00:30:37,000 --> 00:30:38,000
He asked Xue if this was the case.

733
00:30:38,960 --> 00:30:41,240
Xue's face clouded over with anger
after hearing that.

734
00:30:42,200 --> 00:30:43,440
Chunsheng didn't care about this at all

735
00:30:43,640 --> 00:30:45,240
and he asked Xue to make
his attitude clear on the spot.

736
00:30:46,240 --> 00:30:47,000
He said

737
00:30:47,000 --> 00:30:48,000
I'd told him

738
00:30:48,520 --> 00:30:50,400
that Cao Biao had met the criteria
for housing allotment

739
00:30:50,640 --> 00:30:51,680
and asked about Xue's opinion.

740
00:30:52,480 --> 00:30:54,520
Now that he had said this,

741
00:30:54,720 --> 00:30:55,600
I had to support Chunsheng

742
00:30:55,600 --> 00:30:56,840
even if it was hard for me.

743
00:30:57,960 --> 00:30:59,200
Guess what?

744
00:30:59,480 --> 00:31:00,400
Xue said

745
00:31:01,600 --> 00:31:04,400
that as long as I agreed,

746
00:31:04,400 --> 00:31:05,400
Cao could get housing.

747
00:31:05,520 --> 00:31:06,800
He said that
we didn't even need to ask him.

748
00:31:07,360 --> 00:31:08,120
Oh no.

749
00:31:08,200 --> 00:31:09,120
I knew it immediately

750
00:31:09,760 --> 00:31:11,440
that Xue would blame this on me.

751
00:31:11,760 --> 00:31:12,560
Later, Xue left

752
00:31:12,560 --> 00:31:13,920
after having a drink.

753
00:31:14,000 --> 00:31:15,160
He must have been angry.

754
00:31:15,400 --> 00:31:16,720
I asked Chunsheng

755
00:31:17,080 --> 00:31:19,920
why he had to make it so straightforward

756
00:31:19,920 --> 00:31:21,320
without discussing it with me.

757
00:31:21,880 --> 00:31:24,000
I also told him to stay away
from things like this in the future

758
00:31:24,000 --> 00:31:25,440
because he'd offend people.

759
00:31:25,680 --> 00:31:26,680
Guess what he said?

760
00:31:27,640 --> 00:31:28,400
Chunsheng said

761
00:31:29,040 --> 00:31:30,800
people like Xue deserved to be offended.

762
00:31:32,280 --> 00:31:34,040
What can I say then?

763
00:31:42,040 --> 00:31:43,680
For the whole afternoon, I was thinking

764
00:31:44,080 --> 00:31:45,800
about how to make amends.

765
00:31:47,160 --> 00:31:48,080
Shortly before getting off work,

766
00:31:48,080 --> 00:31:49,440
I went to Xue's office.

767
00:31:49,840 --> 00:31:50,920
I told him

768
00:31:51,280 --> 00:31:52,440
that Xiao Chunsheng came up

769
00:31:52,440 --> 00:31:54,360
with this idea on his own.

770
00:31:54,560 --> 00:31:55,880
I said this was the way he is,

771
00:31:56,040 --> 00:31:57,640
please don't take it personally.

772
00:31:58,000 --> 00:31:59,960
But Xue didn't believe me at all.

773
00:31:59,960 --> 00:32:01,160
He said sarcastically

774
00:32:03,200 --> 00:32:04,720
that no subordinates would threaten

775
00:32:04,720 --> 00:32:06,000
their superiors without approval.

776
00:32:06,080 --> 00:32:08,080
He also said that everyone knows
Chunsheng is my friend,

777
00:32:08,400 --> 00:32:09,520
we three

778
00:32:09,720 --> 00:32:10,880
set a trap for him

779
00:32:11,200 --> 00:32:12,560
and I was just shifting the blame.

780
00:32:12,560 --> 00:32:13,800
Of course he wouldn't believe it.

781
00:32:14,640 --> 00:32:15,880
He also claimed

782
00:32:16,080 --> 00:32:17,000
that I was so anxious

783
00:32:17,120 --> 00:32:18,120
to take over his job.

784
00:32:18,440 --> 00:32:19,400
Fang,

785
00:32:20,680 --> 00:32:22,480
I've totally offended Xue.

786
00:32:23,720 --> 00:32:24,480
Wait and see.

787
00:32:24,480 --> 00:32:26,040
I wonder how
he will take revenge in the future.

788
00:32:31,000 --> 00:32:32,200
Every day

789
00:32:33,040 --> 00:32:34,840
I'm very cautious,

790
00:32:35,280 --> 00:32:37,000
yet I somehow got an enemy.

791
00:32:37,800 --> 00:32:38,880
That's so infuriating.

792
00:32:40,560 --> 00:32:41,680
But what can I do?

793
00:32:42,160 --> 00:32:43,080
Who can I blame?

794
00:32:43,480 --> 00:32:44,640
I can't blame Chunsheng, can I?

795
00:32:47,720 --> 00:32:49,160
However, Chunsheng is indeed wrong.

796
00:32:49,480 --> 00:32:51,800
We're adults

797
00:32:51,800 --> 00:32:53,280
and have jobs now.

798
00:32:53,560 --> 00:32:55,080
We have to adapt.

799
00:32:55,480 --> 00:32:56,520
At work,

800
00:32:56,520 --> 00:32:57,760
on paper, I'm his superior,

801
00:32:57,760 --> 00:32:58,880
however, he just does everything

802
00:32:59,280 --> 00:33:00,320
in a straightforward manner
without discussing it with me.

803
00:33:00,720 --> 00:33:01,920
And I can't even criticize him.

804
00:33:02,600 --> 00:33:03,360
Am I right?

805
00:33:05,200 --> 00:33:06,440
Am I right, darling?

806
00:33:08,040 --> 00:33:09,000
What?

807
00:33:10,240 --> 00:33:11,640
So you didn't listen to me?

808
00:33:12,000 --> 00:33:13,320
I mean, the matter I just talked about.

809
00:33:13,760 --> 00:33:14,560
Of course

810
00:33:15,560 --> 00:33:16,920
Xiao Chunsheng is right.

811
00:33:19,280 --> 00:33:21,040
That Mr. Xue abused public power

812
00:33:21,040 --> 00:33:22,480
to retaliate against his colleague.

813
00:33:22,760 --> 00:33:25,440
We should fight against people like him,
shouldn't we?

814
00:33:26,120 --> 00:33:27,400
Yes, we should.

815
00:33:28,120 --> 00:33:30,760
But we also need to be tactical.

816
00:33:31,200 --> 00:33:33,200
What Chunsheng did was not clever.

817
00:33:33,640 --> 00:33:35,760
Isn't this what Xiao Chunsheng
always does?

818
00:33:37,800 --> 00:33:40,800
Hongjun, is today
the first day you know him?

819
00:33:40,960 --> 00:33:42,560
I know the way he is like.

820
00:33:43,000 --> 00:33:45,360
However, people have to change

821
00:33:45,800 --> 00:33:47,040
to adapt to a new environment

822
00:33:47,040 --> 00:33:48,200
and new rules, right?

823
00:33:48,360 --> 00:33:49,800
But what if he just doesn't change?

824
00:33:50,560 --> 00:33:51,760
You want him to change.

825
00:33:52,360 --> 00:33:53,200
Then, let me ask you a question.

826
00:33:53,480 --> 00:33:54,760
When you were determined

827
00:33:54,760 --> 00:33:56,320
to recruit him
to the Anti-smuggling Squad

828
00:33:56,320 --> 00:33:57,680
to be your colleague
despite my objection,

829
00:33:58,320 --> 00:33:59,400
had it ever occurred to you

830
00:33:59,600 --> 00:34:00,960
that the way he does things
would make you unhappy?

831
00:34:01,720 --> 00:34:04,040
Had it ever occurred to you
that he might not change?

832
00:34:05,640 --> 00:34:06,480
Had it?

833
00:34:06,480 --> 00:34:07,360
No!

834
00:34:07,920 --> 00:34:08,670
But it had occurred to me.

835
00:34:10,480 --> 00:34:12,190
That's why I was against it then.

836
00:34:13,040 --> 00:34:14,760
I was afraid that in the end,
you two might fall out.

837
00:34:21,320 --> 00:34:22,880
Well... You made it

838
00:34:22,880 --> 00:34:24,320
sound worse than it actually is.

839
00:34:25,280 --> 00:34:26,710
Actually, it doesn't matter that much.

840
00:34:27,600 --> 00:34:29,440
I can't blame Chunsheng for it.

841
00:34:31,080 --> 00:34:31,960
Of course not.

842
00:34:32,760 --> 00:34:33,960
If Xue wants to take revenge,

843
00:34:34,150 --> 00:34:35,400
then whatever.

844
00:34:37,440 --> 00:34:38,880
Darling,

845
00:34:39,150 --> 00:34:40,670
Chunsheng and I are brothers.

846
00:34:40,880 --> 00:34:42,120
Brothers for life.

847
00:34:42,230 --> 00:34:43,840
No matter whether he changes or not.

848
00:34:44,840 --> 00:34:45,520
I just said this today

849
00:34:45,520 --> 00:34:47,320
because you mentioned this topic.

850
00:34:48,190 --> 00:34:48,920
Anyway,

851
00:34:48,920 --> 00:34:50,630
let's eat.

852
00:34:55,120 --> 00:34:55,800
Really?

853
00:34:57,840 --> 00:34:58,760
