932
00:39:10,000 --> 00:39:11,520
He'd come to see you tomorrow
on Chinese New Year's Day.

933
00:39:11,600 --> 00:39:13,680
But he asked me
to deliver these gifts beforehand

934
00:39:13,920 --> 00:39:16,080
